<html>
    <head>
        <title>글쓰기</title>
        <meta charset = "UTF-8">
        <link rel = "stylesheet" href = "/css/recipe_form.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/nav.css">

        <%-include('script.ejs') %>
    </head>

    <body>
        <%-include('nav.ejs') %>
        <script src="/js/nav.js"></script>

        <form id="write_form" action="/recipe/detail" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <h3>레시피 수정</h3>
            <h4>레시피 제목</h4>
            <input type="text" name="title" class="txtb1" value="<%=result.title%>" required>
            <h4>요리 소개</h4> 
            <textarea name="comment" cols="30" rows="10" class="txtb2"><%=result.comment%></textarea>
            <h4>카테고리</h4>
            <select name="ct_kind" class="txtb3">
                <option value="" selected>종류별</option>
                <option value="kit">간편식</option>
                <option value="soup">국/찌개</option>
                <option value="noodle">면</option>
                <option value="meat">고기</option>
                <option value="seafood">해산물</option>
                <option value="vegetables">채소</option>
                <option value="sauce">소스</option>
                <option value="dessert">디저트</option>
            </select>
            <select name="ct_food" class="txtb3">
                <option value="" selected>재료별</option>
                <option value="beef">소고기</option>
                <option value="meaf">돼지고기</option>
                <option value="chicken">닭고기</option>
                <option value="potato">감자</option>
            </select>
            <p>분류를 바르게 설정해주시면, 사용자들이 쉽게 레시피를 검색할 수 있어요.</p>
            <h4>재료</h4> 
            <textarea name="material" cols="30" rows="10" class="txtb2"><%=result.material%></textarea>
            <h4>요리 순서</h4>
            <% for (let i=0; i<step.length; i++) { %>
                <h4>Step<%=i+1%></h4>
                <textarea name="step_<%=i+1%>" cols="30" rows="10" class="txtb4"><%=step[i]%></textarea>
            <% } %>
            <h4>요리 완성 사진</h4>
            <input type="file" class="imgb" name="userfile" multiple>
            <div class="btn">
                <button class="posting_btn">레시피 수정</button>
                <button type="button" onclick="alertCancel();" class="cancel_btn">취소</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </body>
</html>